kayak fishermen any kayak fishermen out there what kinda yaks do you own and how are they rigged i have a single seat foot peddle powered hobie quest with a lap tiller ft it is absolutely great in still waters or lakes but you still have to be careful not to tip over the are foam core so they won't sink if turned over it's great for fishing the shorelines and submerged trees and stumps or other obstacles i've had mine about years and i wouldn't sell it for any price they are also extremely quiet even while moving so wildlife photography from one of these is the greatest especially early morning when the sun is just coming up and the mist is burning off the water Canoe Kayak Sailing RuneScape skills Swimming USS Tunny (SS-282) Canoe racing Thomas Cole Lake Erie Whitewater kayaking USS Sea Devil (SS-400) USS Wahoo (SS-238) Shaggy dog story Fly fishing Mattress Personal flotation device USS Torsk (SS-423) Tsing Yi Lake Michigan Navassa Island Erie Canal St. Clair River Canoeing Great Dismal Swamp Shipwreck Yellowstone National Park USS Tautog (SS-199) Fire extinguisher Great Lakes Storm of 1913 Nile Montana Welding Hobie cat USS Trigger (SS-237) USS Tang (SS-306) Glycerin Great Lakes Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Effect of Hurricane Katrina on New Orleans Dinghy Fishing Geography of Canada Amazon River The Angry Beavers Renewable energy Anchor Naval mine Whitewater Nuclear power Lake Superior USS Thresher (SS-200) Disaster Great Salt Lake Windsurfing The Waterboys USS Seadragon (SS-194) USS Whale (SS-239) Dam USS S-44 (SS-155) Link (Legend of Zelda) Eggerland series Super Mario 64 Tsunami Upholstery USS S-38 (SS-143) Zambezi Multihull Chernobyl accident Panama Canal Skateboarding trick 1898 invasion of Guant__namo Bay USS Taylor (DD-468) Torpedo USS Trout (SS-202) Geography of Africa Catamaran Ice fishing Lake Pontchartrain Lake Mead Fish farming USS Sea Dog (SS-401) USS Wadsworth (DD-516) Cruising (maritime) Lake Ontario Submarine Seabird Gulf of Mexico Bras d'Or Lake B